# This file is used during python transitions where not all of my packages are
# declared as supported on the new version yet.
# I've tried a few different methods over the years to generate the contents of
# this file, but nothing is ideal. I end up doing it differently every time.

*/* PYTHON_TARGETS: -* python3_14
*/* PYTHON_SINGLE_TARGET: -* python3_14

